{"tid":812441,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"簡大帝：摩佬不適合曼聯","createTime":"2018-09-09T15:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T00:08:23.000Z","uid":114328,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"035853a4c9d5da4d3ecd04c4e72e3b5e2123baa3","tid":812441,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=nI9xU9VHA%2BWZLhKpQvv5Bv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=459468ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】奧脫福大帝簡東拿直言，欣賞現任領隊摩連奴，但他完全不適合曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n從曼聯退役後，52歲的簡東拿（Eric Cantona）轉戰電影圈，至今已有超過25套作品，最近在中國上海、杭州拍攝新戲《Magic》，更要挑戰普通話對白。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「拍戲與足球都一樣，我能勝任，其實我愛足球前，已經愛上了演出，但球技實在太好，所以當足球員。拍了好戲很美好，為曼聯征戰亦很美好。」<br />\n<br />\n為紅魔捧走4次英超，大帝當然仍關心前東家，但坦言不喜歡他們現時的踢法：「沒趣、沒創造力。我喜歡摩連奴，他有很好的性格，但不適合曼聯。」<br />\n<br />\n簡東拿認為，宿敵曼城的主帥哥迪奧拿才是真命天子「曼聯應該找哥帥執教，他應該身在奧脫福，可是正為其他球會施展魔法，一家我不能說出名字的球會。」"},{"pid":"33efcb8c389290ba79ccc16b17bfe10a566503cf","tid":812441,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6780e6cde58b8e13259744fee93a272c7998a225","tid":812441,"uid":41309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"一家我不能說出名字的球會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e03a71390dbabdbd8d128e8e9a5e8663ce05d0","tid":812441,"uid":107611,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6780e6cde58b8e13259744fee93a272c7998a225","tid":812441,"uid":41309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"一家我不能說出名字的球會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"當年背叛列斯聯已經契弟啦，佢怕咩講曼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d92c0e57c70d329f67faefbdfe4a87d5f831904","tid":812441,"uid":161790,"